thread.title: Sheba

author: Sheba
title: Sheba
text: Love this site! Fast, friendly, efficient service. Everything is beautifully done. They go out of their way to make things happen. I ordered my gifts late for my event and they made sure I had next day delivery. I have no doubt that if I'd been in their town I would have had same day. The gift wrapping is superb. This is my third time using them now and my go to place for gifts first. I wish they did a Christmas Club!
